{
  "video_id": "tzJYY2p0QIc",
  "title": "The neuroscience of restorative justice | Dan Reisel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12815.0,
      "end_time": 14450.0,
      "text": "I'd like to talk today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14450.0,
      "end_time": 16922.0,
      "text": "about how we can change our brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16922.0,
      "end_time": 19515.0,
      "text": "and our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19515.0,
      "end_time": 21690.0,
      "text": "Meet Joe."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21690.0,
      "end_time": 25408.0,
      "text": "Joe's 32 years old and a murderer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25408.0,
      "end_time": 28150.0,
      "text": "I met Joe 13 years ago on the lifer wing"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28150.0,
      "end_time": 31970.0,
      "text": "at Wormwood Scrubs high-security prison in London."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31970.0,
      "end_time": 33971.0,
      "text": "I'd like you to imagine this place."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33971.0,
      "end_time": 37680.0,
      "text": "It looks and feels like it sounds:"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37690.0,
      "end_time": 39451.0,
      "text": "Wormwood Scrubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39451.0,
      "end_time": 41675.0,
      "text": "Built at the end of the Victorian Era"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41675.0,
      "end_time": 43187.0,
      "text": "by the inmates themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43187.0,
      "end_time": 46387.0,
      "text": "it is where England's most dangerous prisoners are kept."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46387.0,
      "end_time": 48593.0,
      "text": "These individuals have committed acts"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48593.0,
      "end_time": 50763.0,
      "text": "of unspeakable evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50763.0,
      "end_time": 54474.0,
      "text": "And I was there to study their brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54474.0,
      "end_time": 56226.0,
      "text": "I was part of a team of researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56226.0,
      "end_time": 57903.0,
      "text": "from University College London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57903.0,
      "end_time": 60658.0,
      "text": "on a grant from the U.K. department of health."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60658.0,
      "end_time": 62706.0,
      "text": "My task was to study a group of inmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62706.0,
      "end_time": 65450.0,
      "text": "who had been clinically diagnosed as psychopaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65450.0,
      "end_time": 67175.0,
      "text": "That meant they were the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67175.0,
      "end_time": 68887.0,
      "text": "callous and the most aggressive"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68888.0,
      "end_time": 72120.0,
      "text": "of the entire prison population."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72120.0,
      "end_time": 75589.0,
      "text": "What lay at the root of their behavior?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75589.0,
      "end_time": 79914.0,
      "text": "Was there a neurological cause for their condition?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79915.0,
      "end_time": 82758.0,
      "text": "And if there was a neurological cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82758.0,
      "end_time": 85813.0,
      "text": "could we find a cure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85813.0,
      "end_time": 89758.0,
      "text": "So I'd like to speak about change, and  especially about emotional change."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89758.0,
      "end_time": 91738.0,
      "text": "Growing up, I was always intrigued"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91738.0,
      "end_time": 94801.0,
      "text": "by how people change."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94802.0,
      "end_time": 97325.0,
      "text": "My mother, a clinical psychotherapist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97325.0,
      "end_time": 99965.0,
      "text": "would occasionally see patients at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99965.0,
      "end_time": 101385.0,
      "text": "in the evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101385.0,
      "end_time": 102919.0,
      "text": "She would shut the door to the living room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102919.0,
      "end_time": 104923.0,
      "text": "and I imagined"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104924.0,
      "end_time": 107436.0,
      "text": "magical things happened in that room."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107436.0,
      "end_time": 109117.0,
      "text": "At the age of five or six"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109117.0,
      "end_time": 111559.0,
      "text": "I would creep up in my pajamas"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111559.0,
      "end_time": 114368.0,
      "text": "and sit outside with my ear glued to the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114368.0,
      "end_time": 115815.0,
      "text": "On more than one occasion, I fell asleep"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115815.0,
      "end_time": 117274.0,
      "text": "and they had to push me out of the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117275.0,
      "end_time": 119436.0,
      "text": "at the end of the session."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119436.0,
      "end_time": 122335.0,
      "text": "And I suppose that's how I found myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122335.0,
      "end_time": 124410.0,
      "text": "walking into the secure interview room"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124410.0,
      "end_time": 128418.0,
      "text": "on my first day at Wormwood Scrubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128419.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130755.00000000001,
      "text": "Joe sat across a steel table"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130755.0,
      "end_time": 134981.0,
      "text": "and greeted me with this blank expression."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 134981.0,
      "end_time": 137858.0,
      "text": "The prison warden, looking equally indifferent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137859.0,
      "end_time": 140506.0,
      "text": "said, \"Any trouble, just press the red buzzer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140506.0,
      "end_time": 142945.0,
      "text": "and we'll be around as soon as we can.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142945.0,
      "end_time": 145903.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145903.0,
      "end_time": 147673.0,
      "text": "I sat down."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147673.0,
      "end_time": 150650.0,
      "text": "The heavy metal door slammed shut behind me."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150650.0,
      "end_time": 152744.0,
      "text": "I looked up at the red buzzer"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 152744.0,
      "end_time": 154843.0,
      "text": "far behind Joe on the opposite wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 154843.0,
      "end_time": 157488.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 157489.0,
      "end_time": 159251.0,
      "text": "I looked at Joe."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159251.0,
      "end_time": 161328.0,
      "text": "Perhaps detecting my concern,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 161328.0,
      "end_time": 162684.0,
      "text": "he leaned forward, and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162684.0,
      "end_time": 164911.0,
      "text": "as reassuringly as he could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164911.0,
      "end_time": 166291.0,
      "text": "\"Ah, don't worry about the buzzer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166291.0,
      "end_time": 168543.0,
      "text": "it doesn't work anyway.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168544.0,
      "end_time": 173991.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 175472.0,
      "end_time": 177361.0,
      "text": "Over the subsequent months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 177361.0,
      "end_time": 181446.0,
      "text": "we tested Joe and his fellow inmates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181446.0,
      "end_time": 183497.0,
      "text": "looking specifically at their ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 183497.0,
      "end_time": 188481.0,
      "text": "to categorize different images of emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188481.0,
      "end_time": 190267.0,
      "text": "And we looked at their physical response"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190267.0,
      "end_time": 192900.0,
      "text": "to those emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 192900.0,
      "end_time": 193589.0,
      "text": "So, for example, when most of us look"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193590.0,
      "end_time": 196515.0,
      "text": "at a picture like this of somebody looking sad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 196515.0,
      "end_time": 200650.0,
      "text": "we instantly have a slight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 200660.0,
      "end_time": 202000.0,
      "text": "measurable physical response:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 202000.0,
      "end_time": 205298.0,
      "text": "increased heart rate, sweating of the skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 205298.0,
      "end_time": 207820.0,
      "text": "Whilst the psychopaths in our study were able"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 207820.0,
      "end_time": 209960.0,
      "text": "to describe the pictures accurately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 209960.0,
      "end_time": 212829.0,
      "text": "they failed to show the emotions required."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 212829.0,
      "end_time": 216382.0,
      "text": "They failed to show a physical response."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 216382.0,
      "end_time": 218433.0,
      "text": "It was as though they knew the words"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 218433.0,
      "end_time": 221826.0,
      "text": "but not the music of empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 221826.0,
      "end_time": 223609.0,
      "text": "So we wanted to look closer at this"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 223610.0,
      "end_time": 227590.0,
      "text": "to use MRI to image their brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 227590.0,
      "end_time": 230166.0,
      "text": "That turned out to be not such an easy task."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 230166.0,
      "end_time": 231995.0,
      "text": "Imagine transporting a collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 231995.0,
      "end_time": 234690.0,
      "text": "of clinical psychopaths across central London"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 234690.0,
      "end_time": 236829.0,
      "text": "in shackles and handcuffs"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 236829.0,
      "end_time": 238955.0,
      "text": "in rush hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238955.0,
      "end_time": 242129.0,
      "text": "and in order to place each of them in an MRI scanner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 242129.0,
      "end_time": 244109.0,
      "text": "you have to remove all metal objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 244110.0,
      "end_time": 245444.0,
      "text": "including shackles and handcuffs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 245444.0,
      "end_time": 249798.0,
      "text": "and, as I learned, all body piercings."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249799.0,
      "end_time": 254360.0,
      "text": "After some time, however, we had a tentative answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 254360.0,
      "end_time": 256853.0,
      "text": "These individuals were not just the victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 256853.0,
      "end_time": 258906.0,
      "text": "of a troubled childhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 258906.0,
      "end_time": 261427.0,
      "text": "There was something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 261427.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265470.0,
      "text": "People like Joe have a deficit in a brain area"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 265470.0,
      "end_time": 267108.0,
      "text": "called the amygdala."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 267108.0,
      "end_time": 269132.0,
      "text": "The amygdala is an almond-shaped organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 269132.0,
      "end_time": 272455.0,
      "text": "deep within each of the hemispheres of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 272455.0,
      "end_time": 276940.0,
      "text": "It is thought to be key to the experience of empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 276940.0,
      "end_time": 279846.0,
      "text": "Normally, the more empathic a person is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 279846.0,
      "end_time": 282891.0,
      "text": "the larger and more active their amygdala is."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 282891.0,
      "end_time": 284371.0,
      "text": "Our population of inmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 284371.0,
      "end_time": 285698.0,
      "text": "had a deficient amygdala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 285698.0,
      "end_time": 287993.0,
      "text": "which likely led to their lack of empathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 287993.0,
      "end_time": 290927.0,
      "text": "and to their immoral behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 290927.0,
      "end_time": 294690.0,
      "text": "So let's take a step back."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 294690.0,
      "end_time": 296692.0,
      "text": "Normally, acquiring moral behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 296692.0,
      "end_time": 299820.0,
      "text": "is simply part of growing up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 299820.0,
      "end_time": 301283.0,
      "text": "like learning to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 301283.0,
      "end_time": 304574.0,
      "text": "At the age of six months, virtually every one of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 304574.0,
      "end_time": 308531.0,
      "text": "is able to differentiate between animate and inanimate objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308531.0,
      "end_time": 311500.0,
      "text": "At the age of 12 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 311500.0,
      "end_time": 314229.0,
      "text": "most children are able to imitate"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 314229.0,
      "end_time": 316114.0,
      "text": "the purposeful actions of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 316114.0,
      "end_time": 318649.0,
      "text": "So for example, your mother raises her hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 318649.0,
      "end_time": 321388.0,
      "text": "to stretch, and you imitate her behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 321388.0,
      "end_time": 324589.0,
      "text": "At first, this isn't perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 324589.0,
      "end_time": 326536.0,
      "text": "I remember my cousin Sasha,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 326536.0,
      "end_time": 328699.0,
      "text": "two years old at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 328699.0,
      "end_time": 330359.0,
      "text": "looking through a picture book"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 330359.0,
      "end_time": 333542.0,
      "text": "and licking one finger and flicking the page with the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 333542.0,
      "end_time": 335647.0,
      "text": "licking one finger and flicking the page with the other hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 335647.0,
      "end_time": 337961.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 337961.0,
      "end_time": 341887.0,
      "text": "Bit by bit, we build the foundations  of the social brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 341887.0,
      "end_time": 346519.0,
      "text": "so that by the time we're three, four years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 346519.0,
      "end_time": 347811.0,
      "text": "most children, not all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 347811.0,
      "end_time": 349584.0,
      "text": "have acquired the ability to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 349584.0,
      "end_time": 351187.0,
      "text": "the intentions of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 351187.0,
      "end_time": 354513.0,
      "text": "another prerequisite for empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 354513.0,
      "end_time": 357125.0,
      "text": "The fact that this developmental progression"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 357125.0,
      "end_time": 358627.0,
      "text": "is universal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 358627.0,
      "end_time": 360603.0,
      "text": "irrespective of where you live in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 360603.0,
      "end_time": 363229.0,
      "text": "or which culture you inhabit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 363229.0,
      "end_time": 365442.0,
      "text": "strongly suggests that the foundations"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 365442.0,
      "end_time": 368566.0,
      "text": "of moral behavior are inborn."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 368566.0,
      "end_time": 371420.0,
      "text": "If you doubt this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 371430.0,
      "end_time": 374819.0,
      "text": "try, as I've done, to renege on a promise you've made"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 374819.0,
      "end_time": 376896.0,
      "text": "to a four-year-old."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 376896.0,
      "end_time": 378684.0,
      "text": "You will find that the mind of a four-year old"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 378684.0,
      "end_time": 380188.0,
      "text": "is not naïve in the slightest."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 380188.0,
      "end_time": 383212.0,
      "text": "It is more akin to a Swiss army knife"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 383213.0,
      "end_time": 385244.0,
      "text": "with fixed mental modules"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 385244.0,
      "end_time": 387718.0,
      "text": "finely honed during development"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 387718.0,
      "end_time": 390835.0,
      "text": "and a sharp sense of fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 390835.0,
      "end_time": 393493.0,
      "text": "The early years are crucial."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 393493.0,
      "end_time": 395737.0,
      "text": "There seems to be a window of opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 395737.0,
      "end_time": 398203.0,
      "text": "after which mastering moral questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 398203.0,
      "end_time": 399685.0,
      "text": "becomes more difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 399685.0,
      "end_time": 403819.0,
      "text": "like adults learning a foreign language."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 403819.0,
      "end_time": 405853.0,
      "text": "That's not to say it's impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 405853.0,
      "end_time": 408962.0,
      "text": "A recent, wonderful study from Stanford University"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 408962.0,
      "end_time": 411203.0,
      "text": "showed that people who have played"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 411203.0,
      "end_time": 413611.0,
      "text": "a virtual reality game in which they took on"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413612.0,
      "end_time": 416730.0,
      "text": "the role of a good and helpful superhero"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 416730.0,
      "end_time": 418188.0,
      "text": "actually became more caring and helpful"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 418189.0,
      "end_time": 420692.0,
      "text": "towards others afterwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 420692.0,
      "end_time": 422901.0,
      "text": "Now I'm not suggesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 422901.0,
      "end_time": 425956.0,
      "text": "we endow criminals with superpowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 425956.0,
      "end_time": 429369.0,
      "text": "but I am suggesting that we need to find ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 429369.0,
      "end_time": 431247.0,
      "text": "to get Joe and people like him"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 431247.0,
      "end_time": 433892.0,
      "text": "to change their brains and their behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 433892.0,
      "end_time": 435667.0,
      "text": "for their benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 435667.0,
      "end_time": 438801.0,
      "text": "and for the benefit of the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 438802.0,
      "end_time": 442337.0,
      "text": "So can brains change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 442337.0,
      "end_time": 444921.0,
      "text": "For over 100 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 444921.0,
      "end_time": 448340.0,
      "text": "neuroanatomists and later neuroscientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 448350.0,
      "end_time": 451855.0,
      "text": "held the view that after initial development in childhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 451855.0,
      "end_time": 454279.0,
      "text": "no new brain cells could grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 454279.0,
      "end_time": 455580.0,
      "text": "in the adult human brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 455580.0,
      "end_time": 457670.0,
      "text": "The brain could only change"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 457670.0,
      "end_time": 459490.0,
      "text": "within certain set limits."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 459490.0,
      "end_time": 461147.0,
      "text": "That was the dogma."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 461147.0,
      "end_time": 463385.0,
      "text": "But then, in the 1990s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 463386.0,
      "end_time": 465820.0,
      "text": "studies starting showing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 465820.0,
      "end_time": 467819.0,
      "text": "following the lead of Elizabeth Gould at Princeton and others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 467819.0,
      "end_time": 471154.0,
      "text": "studies started showing the evidence of neurogenesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 471154.0,
      "end_time": 473212.0,
      "text": "the birth of new brain cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 473212.0,
      "end_time": 476281.0,
      "text": "in the adult mammalian brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 476281.0,
      "end_time": 477865.0,
      "text": "first in the olfactory bulb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 477865.0,
      "end_time": 479946.0,
      "text": "which is responsible for our sense of smell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 479946.0,
      "end_time": 481985.0,
      "text": "then in the hippocampus"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 481985.0,
      "end_time": 484290.0,
      "text": "involving short-term memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 484290.0,
      "end_time": 487312.0,
      "text": "and finally in the amygdala itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 487312.0,
      "end_time": 489880.0,
      "text": "In order to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 489880.0,
      "end_time": 491470.0,
      "text": "how this process works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 491470.0,
      "end_time": 493936.0,
      "text": "I left the psychopaths and joined a lab in Oxford"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 493936.0,
      "end_time": 497198.0,
      "text": "specializing in learning and development."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 497198.0,
      "end_time": 500967.0,
      "text": "Instead of psychopaths, I studied mice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 500968.0,
      "end_time": 503309.0,
      "text": "because the same pattern of brain responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 503309.0,
      "end_time": 507390.0,
      "text": "appears across many different species of social animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 507390.0,
      "end_time": 511621.0,
      "text": "So if you rear a mouse in a standard cage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 511621.0,
      "end_time": 514308.0,
      "text": "a shoebox, essentially, with cotton wool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 514308.0,
      "end_time": 515876.0,
      "text": "alone and without much stimulation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 515876.0,
      "end_time": 517486.0,
      "text": "not only does it not thrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 517486.0,
      "end_time": 519243.0,
      "text": "but it will often develop strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 519244.0,
      "end_time": 520818.0,
      "text": "repetitive behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 520818.0,
      "end_time": 523437.0,
      "text": "This naturally sociable animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 523437.0,
      "end_time": 525880.0,
      "text": "will lose its ability to bond with other mice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 525880.0,
      "end_time": 530750.0,
      "text": "even becoming aggressive when introduced to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 530750.0,
      "end_time": 532137.0,
      "text": "However, mice reared in what we called"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 532137.0,
      "end_time": 533642.0,
      "text": "an enriched environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 533643.0,
      "end_time": 535854.0,
      "text": "a large habitation with other mice"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 535854.0,
      "end_time": 539284.0,
      "text": "with wheels and ladders and areas to explore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 539284.0,
      "end_time": 540869.0,
      "text": "demonstrate neurogenesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 540869.0,
      "end_time": 543169.0,
      "text": "the birth of new brain cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 543169.0,
      "end_time": 545483.0,
      "text": "and as we showed, they also perform better"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 545483.0,
      "end_time": 548199.0,
      "text": "on a range of learning and memory tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 548200.0,
      "end_time": 550630.0,
      "text": "Now, they don't develop morality to the point of"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 550630.0,
      "end_time": 552390.0,
      "text": "carrying the shopping bags of little old mice"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 552390.0,
      "end_time": 554611.0,
      "text": "across the street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 554611.0,
      "end_time": 557354.0,
      "text": "but their improved environment results in healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 557354.0,
      "end_time": 559267.0,
      "text": "sociable behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 559267.0,
      "end_time": 562210.0,
      "text": "Mice reared in a standard cage, by contrast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 562210.0,
      "end_time": 564675.0,
      "text": "not dissimilar, you might say, from a prison cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 564675.0,
      "end_time": 567976.0,
      "text": "have dramatically lower levels of new neurons"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 567976.0,
      "end_time": 569603.0,
      "text": "in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 569603.0,
      "end_time": 572419.0,
      "text": "It is now clear that the amygdala of mammals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 572419.0,
      "end_time": 573925.0,
      "text": "including primates like us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 573925.0,
      "end_time": 576436.0,
      "text": "can show neurogenesis."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 576437.0,
      "end_time": 577723.0,
      "text": "In some areas of the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 577723.0,
      "end_time": 581418.0,
      "text": "more than 20 percent of cells are newly formed."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 581418.0,
      "end_time": 583677.0,
      "text": "We're just beginning to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 583677.0,
      "end_time": 585771.0,
      "text": "what exact function these cells have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 585771.0,
      "end_time": 588697.0,
      "text": "but what it implies is that the brain is capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 588697.0,
      "end_time": 593890.0,
      "text": "of extraordinary change way into adulthood."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 593890.0,
      "end_time": 595624.0,
      "text": "However, our brains are also"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 595624.0,
      "end_time": 599264.0,
      "text": "exquisitely sensitive to stress in our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 599264.0,
      "end_time": 601814.0,
      "text": "Stress hormones, glucocorticoids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 601814.0,
      "end_time": 603363.0,
      "text": "released by the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 603364.0,
      "end_time": 606925.0,
      "text": "suppress the growth of these new cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 606925.0,
      "end_time": 609473.0,
      "text": "The more stress, the less brain development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 609473.0,
      "end_time": 613940.0,
      "text": "which in turn causes less adaptability"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 613941.0,
      "end_time": 616684.0,
      "text": "and causes higher stress levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 616684.0,
      "end_time": 620468.0,
      "text": "This is the interplay between nature and nurture"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 620469.0,
      "end_time": 624174.0,
      "text": "in real time in front of our eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 624174.0,
      "end_time": 626241.0,
      "text": "When you think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 626241.0,
      "end_time": 628616.0,
      "text": "it is ironic that our current solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 628616.0,
      "end_time": 630542.0,
      "text": "for people with stressed amygdalae"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 630542.0,
      "end_time": 632334.0,
      "text": "is to place them in an environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 632334.0,
      "end_time": 636662.0,
      "text": "that actually inhibits any chance of further growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 636663.0,
      "end_time": 639150.0,
      "text": "Of course, imprisonment is a necessary part"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 639150.0,
      "end_time": 641569.0,
      "text": "of the criminal justice system"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 641570.0,
      "end_time": 643335.0,
      "text": "and of protecting society."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 643335.0,
      "end_time": 644972.0,
      "text": "Our research does not suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 644972.0,
      "end_time": 647189.0,
      "text": "that criminals should submit their MRI scans"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 647189.0,
      "end_time": 648611.0,
      "text": "as evidence in court"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 648611.0,
      "end_time": 652269.0,
      "text": "and get off the hook because they've got a faulty amygdala."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 652269.0,
      "end_time": 654342.0,
      "text": "The evidence is actually the other way."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 654342.0,
      "end_time": 657193.0,
      "text": "Because our brains are capable of change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 657193.0,
      "end_time": 659691.0,
      "text": "we need to take responsibility for our actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 659691.0,
      "end_time": 661543.0,
      "text": "and they need to take responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 661543.0,
      "end_time": 664971.0,
      "text": "for their rehabilitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 664971.0,
      "end_time": 666775.0,
      "text": "One way such rehabilitation might work"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 666775.0,
      "end_time": 670680.0,
      "text": "is through restorative justice programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 670680.0,
      "end_time": 672396.0,
      "text": "Here victims, if they choose to participate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 672397.0,
      "end_time": 674638.0,
      "text": "and perpetrators meet face to face"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 674638.0,
      "end_time": 677338.0,
      "text": "in safe, structured encounters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 677338.0,
      "end_time": 679168.0,
      "text": "and the perpetrator is encouraged"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 679168.0,
      "end_time": 681137.0,
      "text": "to take responsibility for their actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 681137.0,
      "end_time": 684366.0,
      "text": "and the victim plays an active role in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 684366.0,
      "end_time": 687237.0,
      "text": "In such a setting, the perpetrator can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 687237.0,
      "end_time": 689572.0,
      "text": "perhaps for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 689572.0,
      "end_time": 691976.0,
      "text": "the victim as a real person"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 691976.0,
      "end_time": 693645.0,
      "text": "with thoughts and feelings and a genuine"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 693645.0,
      "end_time": 695483.0,
      "text": "emotional response."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 695483.0,
      "end_time": 697373.0,
      "text": "This stimulates the amygdala"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 697374.0,
      "end_time": 700925.0,
      "text": "and may be a more effective rehabilitative practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 700925.0,
      "end_time": 703991.0,
      "text": "than simple incarceration."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 703991.0,
      "end_time": 705576.0,
      "text": "Such programs won't work for everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 705576.0,
      "end_time": 708265.0,
      "text": "but for many, it could be a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 708265.0,
      "end_time": 712626.0,
      "text": "to break the frozen sea within."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 712626.0,
      "end_time": 715385.0,
      "text": "So what can we do now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 715385.0,
      "end_time": 717896.0,
      "text": "How can we apply this knowledge?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 717897.0,
      "end_time": 720218.0,
      "text": "I'd like to leave you with"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 720218.0,
      "end_time": 721963.0,
      "text": "three lessons that I learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 721963.0,
      "end_time": 724132.0,
      "text": "The first thing that I learned was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 724133.0,
      "end_time": 725659.0,
      "text": "we need to change our mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 725659.0,
      "end_time": 728808.0,
      "text": "Since Wormwood Scrubs was built 130 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 728808.0,
      "end_time": 731923.0,
      "text": "society has advanced in virtually every aspect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 731923.0,
      "end_time": 735337.0,
      "text": "in the way we run our schools, our hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 735337.0,
      "end_time": 737420.0,
      "text": "Yet the moment we speak about prisons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 737420.0,
      "end_time": 740315.0,
      "text": "it's as though we're back in Dickensian times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 740316.0,
      "end_time": 742540.0,
      "text": "if not medieval times."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 742540.0,
      "end_time": 744774.0,
      "text": "For too long, I believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 744774.0,
      "end_time": 748439.0,
      "text": "we've allowed ourselves to be persuaded"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 748439.0,
      "end_time": 751481.0,
      "text": "of the false notion that human  nature cannot change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 751481.0,
      "end_time": 755144.0,
      "text": "and as a society, it's costing us dearly."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 755144.0,
      "end_time": 759200.0,
      "text": "We know that the brain is capable of extraordinary change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 759200.0,
      "end_time": 762590.0,
      "text": "and the best way to achieve that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 762590.0,
      "end_time": 764471.0,
      "text": "even in adults, is to change and modulate"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 764471.0,
      "end_time": 766266.0,
      "text": "our environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 766266.0,
      "end_time": 769151.0,
      "text": "The second thing I have learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 769151.0,
      "end_time": 771776.0,
      "text": "is that we need to create an alliance"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 771777.0,
      "end_time": 775278.0,
      "text": "of people who believe that science is integral"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 775278.0,
      "end_time": 777560.0,
      "text": "to bringing about social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 777560.0,
      "end_time": 780532.0,
      "text": "It's easy enough for a neuroscientist to place"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 780533.0,
      "end_time": 782712.0,
      "text": "a high-security inmate in an MRI scanner."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 782712.0,
      "end_time": 785220.0,
      "text": "Well actually, that turns out not to be so easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 785220.0,
      "end_time": 787879.0,
      "text": "but ultimately what we want to show"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 787879.0,
      "end_time": 791647.0,
      "text": "is whether we're able to reduce the reoffending rates."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 791647.0,
      "end_time": 794368.0,
      "text": "In order to answer complex questions like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 794368.0,
      "end_time": 797190.0,
      "text": "we need people of different backgrounds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 797190.0,
      "end_time": 799223.0,
      "text": "lab-based scientists and clinicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 799223.0,
      "end_time": 801613.0,
      "text": "social workers and policy makers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 801613.0,
      "end_time": 804236.0,
      "text": "philanthropists and human rights activists —"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 804236.0,
      "end_time": 806162.0,
      "text": "to work together."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 806162.0,
      "end_time": 807849.0,
      "text": "Finally, I believe we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 807849.0,
      "end_time": 809487.0,
      "text": "to change our own amygdalae,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 809487.0,
      "end_time": 812267.0,
      "text": "because this issue goes to the heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 812268.0,
      "end_time": 814390.0,
      "text": "not just of who Joe is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 814390.0,
      "end_time": 815951.0,
      "text": "but who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 815951.0,
      "end_time": 818931.0,
      "text": "We need to change our view of Joe"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 818931.0,
      "end_time": 822733.0,
      "text": "as someone wholly irredeemable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 822733.0,
      "end_time": 826242.0,
      "text": "because if we see Joe as wholly irredeemable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 826243.0,
      "end_time": 830523.0,
      "text": "how is he going to see himself as any different?"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 830523.0,
      "end_time": 832394.0,
      "text": "In another decade, Joe will be released"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 832394.0,
      "end_time": 835630.0,
      "text": "from Wormwood Scrubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 835630.0,
      "end_time": 837980.0,
      "text": "Will he be among the 70 percent of inmates"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 837980.0,
      "end_time": 839474.0,
      "text": "who end up reoffending"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 839474.0,
      "end_time": 842256.0,
      "text": "and returning to the prison system?"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 842256.0,
      "end_time": 844891.0,
      "text": "Wouldn't it be better if, while serving his sentence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 844892.0,
      "end_time": 846818.0,
      "text": "Joe was able to train his amygdala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 846818.0,
      "end_time": 849172.0,
      "text": "which would stimulate the growth of new brain cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 849172.0,
      "end_time": 850453.0,
      "text": "and connections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 850453.0,
      "end_time": 853490.0,
      "text": "so that he will be able to face the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 853490.0,
      "end_time": 855169.0,
      "text": "once he gets released?"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 855169.0,
      "end_time": 859633.0,
      "text": "Surely, that would be in the interest of all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 861549.0,
      "end_time": 864800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 864800.0,
      "end_time": 868801.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}